headline: International Business Machines (NYSE:IBM) Partners With Clark Atlanta University For AI Skill Development
summary: International Business Machines (NYSE:IBM) recently announced a partnership with Clark Atlanta University focused on AI education, a move that aligns with the growing demand for tech skills. Over the last quarter, IBM's share price rose 28%, significantly outpacing the market's 2% rise in the past week and highlighting investor optimism. The collaboration may have bolstered confidence in IBM's innovation trajectory. Despite challenges in financial performance, with a drop in net income...
